channel.title: It has been drawn to my intention
channel.description: It's ben drawn to my intention, that Moparscape.org/moparisthebest.org has just became one big flame war. Arn't we supposed to be a community? Every forum I see latly, unless it's posted by Xero or Miss Silabsoft, some in-experienced coder gets flammed when asking a question. Like, they are MoparScape's future. If you agree, please "sign it like a petition" and hopefully we can get a rule about flamming. No doubt I'll be flammed for this, but I don't care.
